---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import H1 from "./H1.astro";
---

<section class="grid grid-cols-9 gap-5 my-6 py-6 px-3 items-center">
  <div class="col-span-9 order-2 lg:order-1 lg:col-span-6">
    <H1 text="About Me" />
    <p class="my-3 text-base text-gray-700">
      Welcome to my portfolio! I'm a passionate full-stack developer with a keen
      eye for crafting immersive web experiences. My toolbox includes a diverse
      array of technologies such as Next.js, Node.js, HTML, CSS, JavaScript,
      React, and Tailwind CSS, among others. With a blend of creativity and
      technical expertise, I specialize in building dynamic, responsive, and
      user-centric web applications.
      <br />
      Let's build something amazing together!
    </p>
  </div>
  <div
    class="lg:order-2 order-1 lg:col-span-3 bg-gray-400 col-span-6 rounded-md overflow-hidden lg:rounded-none shadow-sm lg:shadow-none border"
  >
    <Image
      src="/images/about.png"
      alt="Profile picture"
      width={300}
      height={300}
      class={"w-full h-full"}
    />
  </div>
</section>
